rchive.org/web/20170828230838/https://winteriscoming.net/2017/01/10/liam-cunningham-talks-filming-schedule-game-thrones-season-8/|archivedate=August 28, 2017|df=}}</ref>\n* [[Nathalie Emmanuel]] as [[Missandei]]<ref name=\"IndependentUnderway\">{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-8-filming-cast-belfast-northern-ireland-a8016546.html|title=Game of Thrones season 8 filming looks to be underway as cast members spotted in Belfast|last=Shepherd|first=Jack|date=October 24, 2017|website=The Independent|accessdate=December 18, 2017|url-status = live|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20171024213546/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-8-filming-cast-belfast-northern-ireland-a8016546.html|archivedate=October 24, 2017|df=}}</ref>\n* [[Alfie Allen]] as [[Theon Greyjoy]]<ref name=\"Superherohype\">{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/405667-game-of-thrones-season-8-filming-will-continue-up-until-summer-2018#/slide/1|title=Game of Thrones Season 8 Filming Will Continue Up Until Summer 2018|last=Perry|first=Spencer|date=October 6, 2017|publisher=SuperHeroHype|accessdate=January 25, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125193645/http://www.superherohype.com/news/405667-game-of-thrones-season-8-filming-will-continue-up-until-summer-2018#/slide/1 |archive-date=January 25, 2018 |url-status = live|df=}}</ref>\n* [[John Bradley (English actor)|John Bradley]] as [[Samwell Tarly]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BYYlv56BDey/|title=There's a new tag team in town. \ud83d\udcaa Hope you enjoyed season 7. Thanks for watching and we'll be back. The wait starts now. \ud83d\ude0a #gameofthrones #GOT|last=Bradley|first=John|date=August 29, 2017|work=Instagram|accessdate=December 18, 2017|url-status = live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322154833/https://www.instagram.com/p/BYYlv56BDey/|archivedate=March 22, 2018|df=}}</ref>\n* [[Isaa