spy.com/tv/ustv/a859043/game-of-thrones-season-8-ending-hannah-murray/|title=Game of Thrones' Hannah Murray warns that the show isn't getting a \"fairytale happy ending\"|last=Warner|first=Sam|date=June 8, 2018|work=[[Digital Spy]]|accessdate=February 20, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Carice van Houten]] as [[Melisandre]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-8-melisandre-carice-van-houten-red-woman-trailer-release-date-volantis-a8163571.html|title=Game of Thrones season 8: Melisandre return confirmed as fans theorise on character storyline|last=Stolworthy|first=Jacob|date=January 17, 2018|website=[[The Independent]]|accessdate=January 25, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126012507/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-8-melisandre-carice-van-houten-red-woman-trailer-release-date-volantis-a8163571.html |archive-date=January 26, 2018 |url-status = live|df=}}</ref>\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Recurring cast===\nThe recurring actors listed here are those who appeared in season 8. They are listed by the region in which they first appear.\n{{col-begin|width=67%}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n====In the North====\n* [[Richard Dormer]] as [[Beric Dondarrion]]<ref name=\"Superherohype\"/>\n* [[Ben Crompton]] as [[Eddison Tollett]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/game-of-thrones/news/a842341/game-of-thrones-season-8-cast-dolorous-edd-nights-watch/|title=The Night's Watch WILL be in Game of Thrones season 8, confirms Lord Commander actor|last=McCreesh|first=Louise|date=November 6, 2017|work=[[Digital Spy]]|accessdate=December 18, 2017|url-status = live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206170107/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/game-of-thrones/news/a842341/game-of-thrones-season-8-cast-dolorous-edd-nights-watch/|archivedate=December 6, 2017|df=}}</ref>\n* [[Daniel Portman]] as [[Podrick Payne]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.coupdemainmagazine.com/game-of-thrones/14473|tit